snippet.title: GIANT VS TINY FOOD CHALLENGES || Never-Ending Food For 24 Hours by 123 GO! Live
snippet.description:

Can you survive a giant slice of pizza or you prefer a tiny one. Let's find out in our new video! Challenges with friends are so exciting! There are never too many.
